description:
WELCOME TO NIKE+ TRAINING CLUB – your personal trainer, anywhere, anytime. With over 100 workouts inspired by Nike Master Trainers and world-class athletes you can track your progress and stay motivated to crush your goals.

INTRODUCING WORKOUTS ON THE BIG SCREEN
Bring the studio experience into your living room. Stream N+TC workouts from your phone to a TV or tablet using AirPlay, Chromecast or HDMI cable. 
STAY ON TRACK WITH PROGRAMS
Get lean, get strong, or get toned. Whatever your training goal, commit to a 4-week program and integrate Nike+ Running to reach those goals faster. 

MAKE N+TC YOUR OWN
Take control and only download the workouts you want. Then customize them and choose drills that are right for your body and the way you want to train.

PUSH YOUR PROGRESS
Measure your hard-earned effort and track your progress in NikeFuel, number of workouts, minutes and average calories. 

EARN IT. SHARE IT.
Get motivated with minute milestones and inspirational messages from the club. Share your workouts, achievements and more with your friends.

Now supporting languages for Mexico, Argentina, Brazil, Thailand, Indonesia, Korea, Turkey, USA, UK, Italy, Taiwan, France, Spain, China, Germany, Russia, and Japan.
Need help? Get support at twitter.com/nikesupport
releaseNotes:
- Dual Screen. Stream N+TC workouts from your phone to the TV using AirPlay or an HDMI Cable for iPhone 5 and above.

- Corrected saving and retaining program progress

- Bug fixes and enhancements
